com.joliciel.talismane.machineLearning.features

Class FunctionDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.machineLearning.features.FunctionDescriptor

  • public class FunctionDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object
    A textual descriptor of a function, used for parsing a list of textual function descriptors.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
